  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients are managed clinically according to ad hoc standards and scientific knowledge by a
      multidisciplinary team. Clinical decisions are made after a patient physician discussion.
      Blood and tissue samples are collected. Diagnostic, obstetric management surgical treatment,
      systemic treatment, perinatal results and follow up data are collected.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
